#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Users can request a logout by sending a request to the Quarkus endpoint logout path set with a `quarkus.oidc.logout.path` property.\n"
